Class Rectangle

java.lang.Object
Rectangle
All Implemented Interfaces:
RectangleInterface
public class Rectangle extends Object implements RectangleInterface
A rectangle that stores the (x, y) coordinate of of its top-left corner along with its width and height. The coordinate system used has the origin (0, 0) at the top left with the x-axis going to the right and the y-axes going down.
